{"tid":1565674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人已經好期待10月1號","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T19:03:12.000Z","uid":162480,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7556d88327f8c3c4b443e39d8baed7cad341a2e5","tid":1565674,"uid":162480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"雖然仲有幾個禮拜 <br />\n但係已經好急不及待好想10.1好啲嚟<br />\n好想嗰日可以重現返7.1 8.5發生嘅事<br />\n希望可以再嚟多次全港集會<br />\n<br />\n但係呢幾個星期都一定要出嚟行<br />\n雖然個個星期行都真係冇咩用<br />\n但係原來係呢啲和理非集會嘅過程中<br />\n係會有好多意想不到嘅野出到嚟<br />\n講得多香港人加油 唱得多國歌<br />\n原來係會令香港人呢個民族真正誕生<br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅集會完左<br />\n就係行動升級嘅時候<br />\n希望10.1呢個咁特別嘅日子會係一個觸發點<br />\n有更多人會出嚟<br />\n探望吓林鄭月娥佢話佢僅有嘅野啦"},{"pid":"513d769b21db6a026edc5180afe4472d84e0e063","tid":1565674,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a4bed9bf88a8fb4412dbb468f5baa15eb3847038","tid":1565674,"uid":162480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820a02f7fff24385729ff3e7a4a0492191628b04","tid":1565674,"uid":162480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:47:38.0